:"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: A LONG-EXPECTED PARTY","currentLocation":"Bywater","description":"Hobbit from Bywater who discussed rumors about Frodo's family.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Commented on Frodo's Brandybuck heritage and Bilbo's wealth."},{"name":"Daddy Twofoot","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: A LONG-EXPECTED PARTY","currentLocation":"Bywater","description":"Neighbor of the Gaffer, known for his opinions on local matters.","relationships":[{"character":"Ham Gamgee","relationship":"Neighbor"}],"recentEvents":"Spoke about the Brandybucks and their connection to the Old Forest."},{"name":"Stranger from Michel Delving","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: A LONG-EXPECTED PARTY","currentLocation":"Michel Delving","description":"Visitor from the Westfarthing who speculated about Bilbo's treasure.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Talked about Bilbo's rumored tunnels and wealth."},{"name":"Sandyman","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: A LONG-EXPECTED PARTY","currentLocation":"Hobbiton","description":"Miller who argued about Bilbo's wealth and the rumors surrounding him.","relationships":[{"character":"Ham Gamgee","relationship":"Neighbor"}],"recentEvents":"Disputed the Gaffer's claims about Bilbo's treasure and the Brandybucks."},{"name":"Sackville-Bagginses","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: A LONG-EXPECTED PARTY","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Family of hobbits who scowled at Bilbo's announcement.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Departed in wrath after Bilbo's disappearance."},{"name":"Old Odo Proudfoot","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: A LONG-EXPECTED PARTY","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Hobbit with large, furry feet who commented on Bilbo's disappearance.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Su