e Havens, part of the Council.","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Council member"}],"recentEvents":"Warned of Sauron's potential march on the coasts."},{"name":"Saruman","aliases":["Saruman the White","Saruman the Wise"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE COUNCIL OF ELROND","currentLocation":"Isengard","description":"Former White Wizard turned traitor, seeking to seize the One Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Former colleague and rival"},{"character":"Radagast the Brown","relationship":"Deceived and manipulated"}],"recentEvents":"Captured Gandalf, conspired with the Enemy, and sought to control the Ring."},{"name":"Radagast the Brown","aliases":["Radagast"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE COUNCIL OF ELROND","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Wizard and friend of nature, sent a warning to Gandalf.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Colleague and informant"}],"recentEvents":"Sent a message to Gandalf, then fled Isengard to avoid Saruman's schemes."},{"name":"Gwaihir the Windlord","aliases":["Gwaihir"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE COUNCIL OF ELROND","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Chief of the Great Eagles, rescued Gandalf from Isengard.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Rescuer"}],"recentEvents":"Brought Gandalf to safety after his capture by Saruman."},{"name":"Shadowfax","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE COUNCIL OF ELROND","currentLocation":"Shire","description":"Legendary horse of Rohan, ridden by Gandalf to the Shire.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Rider"}],"recentEvents":"Brought Gandalf to the Shire despite pursuit by the Black Riders."},{"name":"Haldir","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: FAREWE