s to the Company"},{"name":"The Butterbur Family","aliases":["Barliman Butterbur","Mr. Butterbur"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 11: A KNIFE IN THE DARK","currentLocation":"Bree","description":"The family that has kept the inn The Prancing Pony in Bree since ancient times.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Sam Gamgee","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Merry Brandybuck","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Suspicious of"}],"recentEvents":"Lost ponies, arranged for a replacement, and faced accusations of negligence."},{"name":"Gandalf the Grey","aliases":["Gandalf"],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Chapter 5: THE BRIDGE OF KHAZAD-DÛM","currentLocation":"Abyss","description":"A wizard who reappeared after a three-year absence, now warning Frodo about the dangers of the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Friend and advisor"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Friend and confidant"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Friend"},{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Respected companion"},{"character":"Saruman","relationship":"Former colleague and adversary"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Mentor and companion"},{"character":"Boromir","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Gimli son of Glóin","relationship":"Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Fought the Balrog, fell into the abyss, and was lost"},{"name":"Gollum [Sméagol]","aliases":["Sméagol","Gollum"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 9: THE GREAT RIVER","currentLocation":"Following the Company on the river","description":"A corrupted hobbit who possesses the One Ring and is driven by its power.","relationships":[{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Enemy"},{"character":"Déagol","relationship":"Murdered friend"},{"character":"Elves","relationsh