sage through Rohan"}],"recentEvents":"Negotiated with Éomer for horses, searched for Merry and Pippin, encountered the old man in Fangorn"},{"name":"Pippin Took","aliases":["Pippin"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 10: THE BREAKING OF THE FELLOWSHIP","currentLocation":"West bank of the Great River Anduin","description":"Young hobbit companion to Frodo. Expressed curiosity about the Black Rider and the Elves' presence.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Friend and companion"},{"character":"Sam Gamgee","relationship":"Traveling companion"},{"character":"Merry Brandybuck","relationship":"Companion and friend"},{"character":"Tom Bombadil","relationship":"Rescued by"},{"character":"Goldberry","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Companion and protector"},{"character":"Fro,do Baggins","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Advisor"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Meriadoc Brandybuck","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Frodo","relationship":"Companion and friend"},{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Recipient of a silver belt"}],"recentEvents":"Argued with Boromir about Frodo's journey and joined the search for him."},{"name":"Black Riders","aliases":["Black Rider"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 12: FLIGHT TO THE FORD","currentLocation":"River Ford","description":"A tall, dark-cloaked figure pursued Frodo and his companions. Spoke in a strange manner and exhibited unusual sensory abilities.","relationships":[{"character":"Farmer Maggot","relationship":"Encountered"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Pursuers"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Pursued"}],"recentEvents":"Attempt to cross the river, are swept away by the flood, and drown."},{"name":"Gildor Inglorion","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 3: THREE IS COMPA