":"Guest"},{"character":"Merry Brandybuck","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Suspicious of"}],"recentEvents":"Lost ponies, arranged for a replacement, and faced accusations of negligence."},{"name":"Gandalf the Grey","aliases":["Gandalf","Gandalf the White"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 5: THE WHITE RIDER","currentLocation":"Fangorn Forest","description":"A wizard who reappeared after a three-year absence, now warning Frodo about the dangers of the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Friend and advisor"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Friend and confidant"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Friend"},{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Respected companion"},{"character":"Saruman","relationship":"Former colleague and adversary"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Mentor and companion"},{"character":"Boromir","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Gimli son of Glóin","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Revealed his journey to Lothlórien, warned of Saruman's treachery, and discussed the Ents' awakening"},{"name":"Gollum [Sméagol]","aliases":["Sméagol","Gollum"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 9: THE GREAT RIVER","currentLocation":"Following the Company on the river","description":"A corrupted hobbit who possesses the One Ring and is driven by its power.","relationships":[{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Enemy"},{"character":"Déagol","relationship":"Murdered friend"},{"character":"Elves","relationship":"Imprisoned"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Former owner of the Ring"}],"recentEvents":"Followed the Company without being detected."},{"name":"Thorin Oakenshield","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Of the Finding of the Ring","currentLocation":"