acter":"Gimli","relationship":"Quarreled"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allied leader"}],"recentEvents":"Directed the defense of Helm’s Deep, led the charge against the enemy, and coordinated the attack on the gates."},{"name":"Éothain","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE RIDERS OF ROHAN","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Rider of Rohan who mocked the hobbits.","relationships":[{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Questioned lending horses to a Dwarf, witnessed theft of horses"},{"name":"Uglúk","aliases":["Uglúk the Uruk-hai"],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Chapter 3: THE URUK-HAI","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A leader of the Uruk-hai, commanding the Orcs and engaging in conflict with Grishnákh.","relationships":[{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Slain by"}],"recentEvents":"Led the Uruk-hai attack on the Riders of Rohan, was slain in the final battle."},{"name":"Grishnákh","aliases":["Grishnákh the Uruk-hai"],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Chapter 3: THE URUK-HAI","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A subordinate of Uglúk, involved in a power struggle with Uglúk over the Orcs' direction.","relationships":[{"character":"Uglúk","relationship":"Rival commander"}],"recentEvents":"Was killed by an arrow during a skirmish with the Riders of Rohan."},{"name":"Mauhúr","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 3: THE URUK-HAI","currentLocation":"Fangorn Forest","description":"An Orc commander who arrived to aid the Uruk-hai against the Riders of Rohan.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Joined the battle against the Riders of Rohan and was killed in the skirmish."},{"name":"Treebeard","aliases":["Ent"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4: TREEBEARD","currentLocation":"Fangorn Forest","description":"An ancient Ent (tree-being) who guards the forest of Fangorn. Known for his immense size and wisdom.","relationships":[{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Met and conversed with during their journey"},{"character":"Merry Brandybuck","relationship":"Met and conversed with during their journey"},{"character":"Bregalad","relationship":"Comrade"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Carried on his shoulders"},{"character":"Sam Gamgee","relationship":"Carried on his shoulders"}],"recentEvents":"Led the Ents in a march to Isengard to destroy Saruman's stronghold, discussed the Ents' resolve and history."},{"name":"Bregalad","aliases":["Quickbeam"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4: TREEBEARD","currentLocation":"Fangorn Forest","description":"An Ent known for his speed and quickness, who met the hobbits in his ent-house.","relationships":[{"character":"Treebeard","relationship":"Colleague at Entmoot"},{"character":"Merry Brandybuck","relationship":"Hosted in ent-house"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Hosted in ent-house"}],"recentEvents":"Joined the Ents' march to Isengard, expressed eagerness to break Saruman's stronghold."},{"name":"Théoden son of Thengel","aliases":["Third Marshal of Riddermark","Third Marshal of the Mark"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Helm’s Deep","description":"King of the Mark, leading the defense of Helm’s Deep against Saruman's forces.","relationships":[{"character":"Wormtongue","relationship":"Former manipulator"},{"character":"Háma","relationship":"Doorward"},{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Nephew and military leader"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Allied commander"},{"character":"Éowyn","relationship":"Uncle"},{"character":"Éomer","relationship":"Brother"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allied leader"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed the defense of Helm’s Deep, planned to ride out with Aragorn, and inspired the Rid