rond","relationship":"Spouse"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Love interest"}],"recentEvents":"Sang the Elvish song with Elrond and Aragorn"},{"name":"Boromir","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: THE DEPARTURE OF BOROMIR","currentLocation":"River","description":"Companion of the Company, who temporarily succumbed to the Ring's influence.","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Allied"},{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Seeking guidance"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Companion and ally"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Companion and fellow traveler"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Companion and fellow traveler"},{"character":"Frodo","relationship":"Companion and friend"},{"character":"Galad,riel","relationship":"Recipient of a golden belt"}],"recentEvents":"Died defending Frodo and Sam, funeral rites performed"},{"name":"Gimli son of Glóin","aliases":["Glóin","Gimli"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Road to Isengard","description":"A dwarf of important appearance, richly dressed with a white beard and silver belt, part of the twelve companions of Thorin Oakenshield.","relationships":[{"character":"Gimli son of Glóin","relationship":"Father"},{"character":"Elrand","relationship":"Advisor"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Conversation about the Ring and dwarven affairs"},{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Respected"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Companion and friend"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Companion and friend"},{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Recipient of golden hair strands"},{"character":"Boromir","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Háma","relationship":"Laid his axe beside the sword"},{"character":"Éomer","relationship":"Quarreled"},{"character":"Legolas 