d of Sauron's potential march on the coasts."},{"name":"Saruman","aliases":["Saruman the White","Saruman the Wise"],"importance":"secondary","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: THE ROAD TO ISENGARD","currentLocation":"Isengard","description":"The wizard whose stronghold was destroyed by the Ents and the company","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Former colleague and rival"},{"character":"Radagast the Brown","relationship":"Deceived and manipulated"},{"character":"Treebeard","relationship":"Opponent"}],"recentEvents":"His stronghold was overthrown, his power defeated"},{"name":"Radagast the Brown","aliases":["Radagast"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE COUNCIL OF ELROND","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Wizard and friend of nature, sent a warning to Gandalf.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Colleague and informant"}],"recentEvents":"Sent a message to Gandalf, then fled Isengard to avoid Saruman's schemes."},{"name":"Gwaihir the Windlord","aliases":["Gwaihir"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE COUNCIL OF ELROND","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Chief of the Great Eagles, rescued Gandalf from Isengard.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Rescuer"}],"recentEvents":"Brought Gandalf to safety after his capture by Saruman."},{"name":"Shadowfax","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Helm’s Deep","description":"Legendary horse of Rohan, ridden by Gandalf to the Shire.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Rider"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Ran alongside Aragorn and the Riders during the final charge"},{"name":"Haldir","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","