nown for spreading false information.","relationships":[{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Former advisor"},{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Confronted about false reports"}],"recentEvents":"Forced to leave Edoras, exposed as a traitor, and sent away by Théoden"},{"name":"Éowyn daughter of Éomund","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 6: THE KING OF THE GOLDEN HALL","currentLocation":"Edoras","description":"Sister of Éomer, declared Lady of the Mark","relationships":[{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Niece"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Affianced"}],"recentEvents":"Received royal sword and corslet, stood guard at the Golden Hall"},{"name":"Gamling","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Helm’s Deep","description":"Rider of the Mark, fought in the battle to defend Helm’s Deep","relationships":[{"character":"Gimli son of Glóin","relationship":"Collaborated in blocking the culvert"},{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Rider of the Mark"}],"recentEvents":"Blocked the culvert with Gimli, fought in the battle, and assisted in the final charge"},{"name":"Ceorl","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Helm’s Deep","description":"Rider who reported to Théoden about the state of the battle at Helm’s Deep.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Informed Théoden of the enemy's advance and the fate of Erkenbrand."},{"name":"Erkenbrand","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Road to Isengard","description":"Lord of Westfold, arrived with reinforcements during the battle","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Allied commander"},{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Allied"}],"recentEvents":"Leading the Men of the Mark