","relationships":[{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Enemy"},{"character":"Déagol","relationship":"Murdered friend"},{"character":"Elves","relationship":"Imprisoned"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Former owner of the Ring"}],"recentEvents":"Followed the Company without being detected."},{"name":"Thorin Oakenshield","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Of the Finding of the Ring","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Leader of the dwarves on a quest for treasure, slain in the Battle of Five Armies.","relationships":[{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Enemy"}],"recentEvents":"Died in the Battle of Five Armies, with his hoard destroyed."},{"name":"Ham Gamgee","aliases":["the Gaffer"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: A LONG-EXPECTED PARTY","currentLocation":"Bywater","description":"Old gardener and friend of Bilbo and Frodo, known for his tales of Bilbo's wealth.","relationships":[{"character":"Sam Gamgee","relationship":"Father"},{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Friend"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Friend"}],"recentEvents":"Spoke about Bilbo's treasure, discussed the party, and interacted with guests."},{"name":"Sam Gamgee","aliases":["Sam","the Gaffer"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4: TREEBEARD","currentLocation":"Fangorn Forest","description":"Frodo's loyal gardener and companion. Noted the Black Rider's presence and provided crucial information about the stranger in Hobbiton.","relationships":[{"character":"Ham Gamgee","relationship":"Father"},{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Friend"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Travel companion and loyal friend"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Companion and friend"},{"character":"Fro, Baggins","relationship":"Traveling companion"},{"character":"Tom Bombadil","relationship":"Rescued by"},{"character":"Goldberry","relationship":"Guest"},{"cha