"currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven guard of Lothlórien, guided the Company to Caras Galadhon.","relationships":[{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Elven kin"},{"character":"Rúmil","relationship":"Elven companion"},{"character":"Orophin","relationship":"Elven companion"},{"character":"Gimli son of Glóin","relationship":"Guide"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Guide"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Guide"},{"character":"Celeborn","relationship":"Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Guided the Company out of Lothlórien, spoke of the dangers ahead"},{"name":"Rúmil","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 6: LOTHLÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven guard of Lórien, part of the Galadhrim","relationships":[{"character":"Haldir","relationship":"Elven companion"}],"recentEvents":"Assisted in guarding the Company, crossed the river with ropes, and discussed the Company's journey"},{"name":"Orophin","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 6: LOTHLÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven guard of Lórien, part of the Galadhrim","relationships":[{"character":"Haldir","relationship":"Elven companion"},{"character":"Rúmil","relationship":"Elven companion"}],"recentEvents":"Assisted in guarding the Company, crossed the river with ropes, and discussed the Company's journey"},{"name":"Celeborn","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: FAREWELL TO LÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven lord who accompanied Galadriel and led the Company back to the hythe.","relationships":[{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Led the Company back to the hythe and participated in the farewell ceremony."},{"name":"Galadriel","aliases":["Lady Galadriel"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: FAREWELL TO LÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlór