ney to Isengard"},{"name":"Éothain","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE RIDERS OF ROHAN","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Rider of Rohan who mocked the hobbits.","relationships":[{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Questioned lending horses to a Dwarf, witnessed theft of horses"},{"name":"Uglúk","aliases":["Uglúk the Uruk-hai"],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Chapter 3: THE URUK-HAI","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A leader of the Uruk-hai, commanding the Orcs and engaging in conflict with Grishnákh.","relationships":[{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Slain by"}],"recentEvents":"Led the Uruk-hai attack on the Riders of Rohan, was slain in the final battle."},{"name":"Grishnákh","aliases":["Grishnákh the Uruk-hai"],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Chapter 3: THE URUK-HAI","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A subordinate of Uglúk, involved in a power struggle with Uglúk over the Orcs' direction.","relationships":[{"character":"Uglúk","relationship":"Rival commander"}],"recentEvents":"Was killed by an arrow during a skirmish with the Riders of Rohan."},{"name":"Mauhúr","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 3: THE URUK-HAI","currentLocation":"Fangorn Forest","description":"An Orc commander who arrived to aid the Uruk-hai against the Riders of Rohan.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Joined the battle against the Riders of Rohan and was killed in the skirmish."},{"name":"Treebeard","aliases":["Bregalad","Ent","Quickbeam"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 11: THE PALANTÍR","currentLocation":"Isengard","description":"An ancient Ent (tree-being) who guards the forest of Fangorn. Known for his immense size and wisdom.","relationships":[{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Met and conversed with during their journey"},{"character":"Me