d friend"},{"character":"Glorfindel","relationship":"Allied warrior"},{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Advisor"},{"character":"Arwen","relationship":"Love interest"},{"character":"Boromir","relationship":"Companion and fellow traveler"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Traveling companion"},{"character":"Gimli son of Glóin","relationship":"Companion and friend"},{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Recipient of the Elfstone brooch"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Negotiating for passage through Rohan"},{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"King of the Mark"},{"character":"Éowyn","relationship":"Affianced"},{"character":"Éomer","relationship":"Allied leader"},{"character":"Gandalf the White","relationship":"Mentor and companion"},{"character":"Legolas Greenleaf","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Advisor"},{"character":"Treebeard","relationship":"Allied with"}],"recentEvents":"Fought Saruman at Orthanc, witnessed the destruction of the palantír, remained concerned for Frodo and Sam"},{"name":"Pippin Took","aliases":["Pippin"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 11: THE PALANTÍR","currentLocation":"With Gandalf en route to Minas Tirith","description":"A hobbit who joined the company of the Ring and was presumed lost but was found feasting in Isengard","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Friend and companion"},{"character":"Sam Gamgee","relationship":"Traveling companion"},{"character":"Merry Brandybuck","relationship":"Close friend and companion"},{"character":"Tom Bombadil","relationship":"Rescued by"},{"character":"Goldberry","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Companion and protector"},{"character":"Fro,do Baggins","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Advisor"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Meriadoc Brandybuck","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Frodo","relationship":"Companion and friend"},{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Recipient of a silver belt"},{"character":"Treebeard","relationship":"Met and conversed with during their journey"},{"character":"Gimli son of Glóin","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Legolas Greenleaf","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Merry","relationship":"Cousin"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Mentor"},{"character":"Gandalf the White","relationship":"Mentor and guardian"}],"recentEvents":"Conversation with Gandalf about the Palantír, Nazgûl, and the journey"},{"name":"Black Riders","aliases":["Black Rider"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4: TREEBEARD","currentLocation":"River Ford","description":"A tall, dark-cloaked figure pursued Frodo and his companions. Spoke in a strange manner and exhibited unusual sensory abilities.","relationships":[{"character":"Farmer Maggot","relationship":"Encountered"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Pursuers"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Pursued"}],"recentEvents":"Continued pursuit of the hobbits through the forest"},{"name":"Gildor Inglorion","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 3: THREE IS COMPANY","currentLocation":"Green hall","description":"Leader of a group of Elves who encountered Frodo and his companions. Identified himself as of the House of Finrod.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Advisor and conversant"}],"recentEvents":"Advised Frodo to flee the Shire, warned of the Black Riders, and encouraged him to seek Gandalf's counsel."},{"name":"Farmer Maggot","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: IN THE HOUSE OF TOM BOMBADIL","currentLocation":"Old Forest","description":"Local farmer who provided Tom Bombadil with information about Frodo's journey.","relationships":[{"character":"Pippi