"},{"character":"Sam Gamgee","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Merry Brandybuck","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Suspicious of"}],"recentEvents":"Lost ponies, arranged for a replacement, and faced accusations of negligence."},{"name":"Gandalf the White","aliases":["Gandalf","Gandalf the Grey"],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Chapter 5: THE WINDOW ON THE WEST","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A wizard who reappeared after a three-year absence, now warning Frodo about the dangers of the Ring.","relationships":[{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Friend and advisor"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Leader of the Fellowship"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Respected companion"},{"character":"Saruman","relationship":"Former colleague and adversary"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Mentor and companion"},{"character":"Boromir","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Gimli son of Glóin","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Advisor and mentor"},{"character":"Háma","relationship":"Debated entry protocols"},{"character":"Wormtongue","relationship":"Opponent and former manipulator"},{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Allies in the war effort"},{"character":"Treebeard","relationship":"Collaborated to defeat Saruman"},{"character":"Théoden","relationship":"Allied ruler of Rohan"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Mentor and guardian"}],"recentEvents":"Frodo claims to have seen him fall into the abyss, contradicting earlier accounts of his survival"},{"name":"Gollum [Sméagol]","aliases":["Sméagol","Gollum"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 6: THE FORBIDDEN POOL","currentLocation":"Henneth Annûn","description":"A former hobbi