 against wolves and Wargs"},{"name":"Glorfindel","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE COUNCIL OF ELROND","currentLocation":"Rivendell","description":"Elven lord and warrior, advocate for the Ring's destruction.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Rescuer"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Allied warrior"},{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Lord and companion"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allied warrior"}],"recentEvents":"Argued for the Ring's destruction to prevent Sauron's return."},{"name":"Elrond","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 3: THE RING GOES SOUTH","currentLocation":"High moor","description":"Elven lord and leader of the Council, advocate for the Ring's destruction.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Patient"},{"character":"Glorfindel","relationship":"Lord and companion"},{"character":"Arwen","relationship":"Spouse"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allied"},{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Respected advisor"},{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"ally"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Advisor"}],"recentEvents":"Delivered farewell speech, outlined the quest's terms."},{"name":"Arwen","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: MANY MEETINGS","currentLocation":"Rivendell","description":"Elven princess and daughter of Elrond","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Spouse"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Love interest"}],"recentEvents":"Sang the Elvish song with Elrond and Aragorn"},{"name":"Boromir","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: THE DEPARTURE OF BOROMIR","currentLocation":"River","description":"Companion of the Company, who temporarily succumbed to the Ring's influence.","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Allied"},{"character":"Gandalf the Gr