cholar and advisor, part of the Council.","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Allied"}],"recentEvents":"Participated in debates about the Ring's fate."},{"name":"Galdor of the Havens","aliases":["Galdor"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE COUNCIL OF ELROND","currentLocation":"Rivendell","description":"Elven lord from the Havens, part of the Council.","relationships":[{"character":"Elrond","relationship":"Council member"}],"recentEvents":"Warned of Sauron's potential march on the coasts."},{"name":"Saruman","aliases":["Saruman the White","Saruman the Wise"],"importance":"secondary","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"Chapter 10: THE VOICE OF SARUMAN","currentLocation":"Orthanc","description":"The wizard whose stronghold was destroyed by the Ents and the company","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Former colleague and rival"},{"character":"Radagast the Brown","relationship":"Deceived and manipulated"},{"character":"Treebeard","relationship":"Opponent"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Former colleague"},{"character":"Gríma Wormtongue","relationship":"Former subordinate"}],"recentEvents":"Confronted Gandalf, attempted to manipulate Théoden, had his staff broken"},{"name":"Radagast the Brown","aliases":["Radagast"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE COUNCIL OF ELROND","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Wizard and friend of nature, sent a warning to Gandalf.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Colleague and informant"}],"recentEvents":"Sent a message to Gandalf, then fled Isengard to avoid Saruman's schemes."},{"name":"Gwaihir the Windlord","aliases":["Gwaihir"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 2: THE COUNCIL OF ELROND","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Chief of the Great Eagles, rescued Gandalf from Isengard.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Rescuer"}],"recentEvents":"Brought Gandalf to safety after his capture by Saruman."},{"name":"Shadowfax","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Helm’s Deep","description":"Legendary horse of Rohan, ridden by Gandalf to the Shire.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Rider"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Ran alongside Aragorn and the Riders during the final charge"},{"name":"Haldir","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: FAREWELL TO LÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven guard of Lothlórien, guided the Company to Caras Galadhon.","relationships":[{"character":"Legolas","relationship":"Elven kin"},{"character":"Rúmil","relationship":"Elven companion"},{"character":"Orophin","relationship":"Elven companion"},{"character":"Gimli son of Glóin","relationship":"Guide"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Guide"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Guide"},{"character":"Celeborn","relationship":"Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Guided the Company out of Lothlórien, spoke of the dangers ahead"},{"name":"Rúmil","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 6: LOTHLÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven guard of Lórien, part of the Galadhrim","relationships":[{"character":"Haldir","relationship":"Elven companion"}],"recentEvents":"Assisted in guarding the Company, crossed the river with ropes, and discussed the Company's journey"},{"name":"Orophin","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 6: LOTHLÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven guard of Lórien, part of the Galadhrim","relationships":[{"character":"Haldir","relationship":"Elven companion"},{"character":"Rúmil","relationship":"Elven companion"}],"recentEvents":"Assisted in guarding the Company, crossed the river with ropes, and discussed the Company's journey"},{"name":"Celeborn","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: FAREWELL TO LÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven lord who accompanied Galadriel and led the Company back to the hythe.","relationships":[{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Led the Company back to the hythe and participated in the farewell ceremony."},{"name":"Galadriel","aliases":["Lady Galadriel"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: FAREWELL TO LÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven queen who bestowed gifts and delivered a farewell speech to the Company.","relationships":[{"character":"Celeborn","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Hosted in her realm and tested through the Mirror"},{"character":"Sam Gamgee","relationship":"Hosted in her realm and tested through the Mirror"}],"recentEvents":"Gave gifts to Aragorn, Boromir, Merry, Pippin, Legolas, Sam, and Gimli; delivered a farewell speech and sang an Elvish song."},{"name":"Éomer son of Éomund","aliases":["Third Marshal of Riddermark","Third Marshal of the Mark"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Road to Isengard","description":"Commander of the Rohirrim, leading the defense of Helm’s Deep.","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Lent horses"},{"character":"Éothain","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Brother"},{"character":"Gimli","relationship":"Quarreled"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allied leader"},{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Allied"}],"recentEvents":"Joining Théoden's company, discussing the journey to Isengard"},{"name":"Éothain","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status"