aracter":"Treebeard","relationship":"Colleague at Entmoot"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Carried on his shoulders"},{"character":"Sam Gamgee","relationship":"Carried on his shoulders"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Collaborated to defeat Saruman"},{"character":"Gandalf the White","relationship":"Respected companion"}],"recentEvents":"Observed the group passing through Isengard before they departed"},{"name":"Théoden son of Thengel","aliases":["Théoden","Third Marshal of Riddermark","Third Marshal of the Mark"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 11: THE PALANTÍR","currentLocation":"En route to Helm’s Deep","description":"King of the Mark, leading the defense of Helm’s Deep against Saruman's forces.","relationships":[{"character":"Wormtongue","relationship":"Former manipulator"},{"character":"Háma","relationship":"Doorward"},{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Nephew and military leader"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Allied commander"},{"character":"Éowyn","relationship":"Uncle"},{"character":"Éomer","relationship":"Brother"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Allied leader"},{"character":"Gandalf the White","relationship":"Advisor"},{"character":"Gandalf","relationship":"Allied ruler"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed the group's route and warned of Saruman's pursuit"},{"name":"Háma","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Under the Hornburg","description":"Servant of Théoden, previously untrustworthy but now tasked with errands","relationships":[{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Subordinate"},{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Debated entry protocols"},{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Delivered sword to"},{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Advisor"}],"recentEvents":"Killed in battle, buried under the Hornburg"},{"name":"Wormtongue [Gríma son of 