gee","relationship":"Father"},{"character":"Bilbo Baggins","relationship":"Friend"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Travel companion and loyal friend"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Companion and friend"},{"character":"Fro, Baggins","relationship":"Traveling companion"},{"character":"Tom Bombadil","relationship":"Rescued by"},{"character":"Goldberry","relationship":"Guest"},{"character":"Strider","relationship":"Suspicious of"},{"character":"Merry Brandybuck","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Mentor"},{"character":"Frodo","relationship":"Companion and friend"},{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Visited by Galadriel in her realm"},{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Leader of the Company"},{"character":"Gollum","relationship":"Suspicious of Gollum's true intentions but forced to rely on him"},{"character":"Faramir","relationship":"Captured by soldiers"}],"recentEvents":"Fought Shelob's web, aided Frodo in breaking her web, and fled the lair."},{"name":"Old Noakes","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: A LONG-EXPECTED PARTY","currentLocation":"Bywater","description":"Hobbit from Bywater who discussed rumors about Frodo's family.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Commented on Frodo's Brandybuck heritage and Bilbo's wealth."},{"name":"Daddy Twofoot","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: A LONG-EXPECTED PARTY","currentLocation":"Bywater","description":"Neighbor of the Gaffer, known for his opinions on local matters.","relationships":[{"character":"Ham Gamgee","relationship":"Neighbor"}],"recentEvents":"Spoke about the Brandybucks and their connection to the Old Forest."},{"name":"Stranger from Michel Delving","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: A LONG-EXPECTED PARTY","currentLocation":"Michel Delving","description":"Visitor from the Westfarthing who speculated a