ription":"Leader of a group of Elves who encountered Frodo and his companions. Identified himself as of the House of Finrod.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Advisor and conversant"}],"recentEvents":"Advised Frodo to flee the Shire, warned of the Black Riders, and encouraged him to seek Gandalf's counsel."},{"name":"Farmer Maggot","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: IN THE HOUSE OF TOM BOMBADIL","currentLocation":"Old Forest","description":"Local farmer who provided Tom Bombadil with information about Frodo's journey.","relationships":[{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Friend"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Unaware of his identity"},{"character":"Tom Bombadil","relationship":"Informant"}],"recentEvents":"Shared details about Frodo's flight with Tom Bombadil."},{"name":"Grip","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","description":"One of Farmer Maggot's dogs.","recentEvents":"Barked at the travelers.","relationships":[]},{"name":"Fang","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","description":"One of Farmer Maggot's dogs.","recentEvents":"Barked at the travelers.","relationships":[]},{"name":"Wolf","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","description":"One of Farmer Maggot's dogs.","recentEvents":"Barked at the travelers.","relationships":[]},{"name":"Fatty Bolger","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 11: A KNIFE IN THE DARK","currentLocation":"Bree","description":"A hobbit from Buckland who witnesses the attack on Crickhollow and flees the scene.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Neighbor"}],"recentEvents":"Notified enemies in Buckland, fled to a distant house, and cried about being targeted."},{"name":"Fredegar","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 5: A CONSPIRACY UNMASKED","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Hobbit who remains behind in