condary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Helm’s Deep","description":"Rider of the Mark, fought in the battle to defend Helm’s Deep","relationships":[{"character":"Gimli son of Glóin","relationship":"Collaborated in blocking the culvert"},{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Rider of the Mark"}],"recentEvents":"Blocked the culvert with Gimli, fought in the battle, and assisted in the final charge"},{"name":"Ceorl","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Helm’s Deep","description":"Rider who reported to Théoden about the state of the battle at Helm’s Deep.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Informed Théoden of the enemy's advance and the fate of Erkenbrand."},{"name":"Erkenbrand","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Road to Isengard","description":"Lord of Westfold, arrived with reinforcements during the battle","relationships":[{"character":"Aragorn son of Arathorn","relationship":"Allied commander"},{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Allied"}],"recentEvents":"Leading the Men of the Mark, overseeing the handling of Dunland captives"},{"name":"Isengard","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"unknown","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: THE ROAD TO ISENGARD","currentLocation":"Isengard","description":"The ruined stronghold of Saruman, now under the control of the Ents","relationships":[]},{"name":"Men from the South","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 3: THE BLACK GATE IS CLOSED","currentLocation":"Near the Black Gate","description":"Warriors in red and gold, bearing round shields and spears with red tips","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Observed by Gollum and Sam, described as approaching Mordor"},{"name":"Faramir","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: MINAS TIRITH","currentLocation":"Ithilien","description":"Captain of Gondor, known for his wisdom and honor, engages in deep conversation with Frodo and Sam about the Ring and his brother Boromir.","relationships":[{"character":"Mablung","relationship":"Comrade"},{"character":"Damrod","relationship":"Comrade"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Suspects Frodo of hiding the Ring’s history"},{"character":"Boromir","relationship":"Brother who died under mysterious circumstances"},{"character":"Samwise Gamgee","relationship":"Respected companion"},{"character":"Gollum","relationship":"Warned about the creature's dangers"},{"character":"Sam Gamgee","relationship":"Mentor figure"}],"recentEvents":"Return to Minas Tirith"},{"name":"Mablung","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 5: THE WINDOW ON THE WEST","currentLocation":"Ithilien","description":"Gondor soldier accompanying Faramir and Frodo","relationships":[{"character":"Faramir","relationship":"Comrade in Gondor’s forces"},{"character":"Damrod","relationship":"Comrade"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Guardian during the interrogation"}],"recentEvents":"Participated in the secret camp setup with Faramir and Damrod"},{"name":"Damrod","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 5: THE WINDOW ON THE WEST","currentLocation":"Ithilien","description":"Soldier of Gondor, Ranger of Ithilien, spoke in elven-tongue","relationships":[{"character":"Faramir","relationship":"Comrade in Gondor’s forces"},{"character":"Mablung","relationship":"Comrade"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Guardian during the interrogation"}],"recentEvents":"Participated in the secret camp setup with Faram, Mablung, and Frodo"},{"name":"Mûmak","aliases":["Oliphaunt"],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4: OF HERBS AND STEWED RABBIT","currentLocation":"Ithilien","description":"A massive creature of Harad, part of the battle","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Participated in the battle against Southrons"},{"name":"Samwise Gamgee","aliases":["Sam"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 10: THE CHOICES OF MASTER SAMWISE","currentLocation":"Near Cirith Ungol","description":"Frodo's loyal gardener and companion, carrying provisions and providing support.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Companion and Ring-bearer"},{"character":"Faramir","relationship":"Respects Faramir’s authority but challenges his accusations"},{"character":"Gollum","relationship":"Fighting"}],"recentEvents":"Fought Orcs to save Frodo, discovered Frodo was alive but captured"},{"name":"Anborn","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 6: THE FORBIDDEN POOL","currentLocation":"Henneth Annûn","description":"A scout under Faramir's command, reports unusual sightings in the wilderness.","relationships":[{"character":"Faramir","relationship":"Ordered to escort Gollum"}],"recentEvents":"Took Gollum away from Frodo and Faramir."},{"name":"Shelob","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 9: SHELOB’S LAIR","currentLocation":"Shelob’s Lair (Torech Ungol)","description":"A giant spider and predator, dwells in the dark tunnels near Cirith Ungol.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Attacking"}],"recentEvents":"Chased Frodo down the path, nearly capturing him"},{"name":"Denethor","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: MINAS TIRITH","currentLocation":"Minas Tirith","description":"Steward of Gondor, ruler of Minas Tirith, engaged in political and military strategy","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the White","relationship":"Advisor and correspondent"},{"character":"Boromir","relationship":"Father (deceased)"},{"character":"Pippin Took","relationship":"Father figure figure/ally"}],"recentEvents":"Summoned Pippin"},{"name":"Ingold","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 1: M