ter":"Haldir","relationship":"Elven companion"}],"recentEvents":"Assisted in guarding the Company, crossed the river with ropes, and discussed the Company's journey"},{"name":"Orophin","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 6: LOTHLÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven guard of Lórien, part of the Galadhrim","relationships":[{"character":"Haldir","relationship":"Elven companion"},{"character":"Rúmil","relationship":"Elven companion"}],"recentEvents":"Assisted in guarding the Company, crossed the river with ropes, and discussed the Company's journey"},{"name":"Celeborn","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: FAREWELL TO LÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven lord who accompanied Galadriel and led the Company back to the hythe.","relationships":[{"character":"Galadriel","relationship":"Companion"}],"recentEvents":"Led the Company back to the hythe and participated in the farewell ceremony."},{"name":"Galadriel","aliases":["Lady Galadriel"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 8: FAREWELL TO LÓRIEN","currentLocation":"Lothlórien","description":"Elven queen who bestowed gifts and delivered a farewell speech to the Company.","relationships":[{"character":"Celeborn","relationship":"Companion"},{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Hosted in her realm and tested through the Mirror"},{"character":"Sam Gamgee","relationship":"Hosted in her realm and tested through the Mirror"}],"recentEvents":"Gave gifts to Aragorn, Boromir, Merry, Pippin, Legolas, Sam, and Gimli; delivered a farewell speech and sang an Elvish song."},{"name":"Éomer son of Éomund","aliases":["Third Marshal of Riddermark","Third Marshal of the Mark"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Road to Isengard","description":"Commander of the Rohirrim, leading the defense of Helm’s Deep.","relationships":[{"character":"A