onship":"Negotiated with the Wild Man"}],"recentEvents":"Blowed a horn to rally Rohan, led a charge against Mordor's forces, rode Snowmane into battle."},{"name":"Háma","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","currentLocation":"Under the Hornburg","description":"Servant of Théoden, previously untrustworthy but now tasked with errands","relationships":[{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Subordinate"},{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Debated entry protocols"},{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Delivered sword to"},{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Advisor"}],"recentEvents":"Killed in battle, buried under the Hornburg"},{"name":"Wormtongue [Gríma son of Gálmód]","aliases":["Gríma son of Gálmód","Wormtongue"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 10: THE VOICE OF SARUMAN","currentLocation":"In the flood near Orthanc","description":"Cunning advisor to Théoden, known for spreading false information.","relationships":[{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Former advisor"},{"character":"Gandalf the Grey","relationship":"Confronted about false reports"},{"character":"Saruman","relationship":"Loyal to"},{"character":"Théoden","relationship":"Former counsellor"}],"recentEvents":"Threw the crystal ball at the group"},{"name":"Éowyn daughter of Éomund","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 3: THE MUSTER OF ROHAN","currentLocation":"Dunharrow","description":"Warrior woman clad in armor, daughter of Éomund","relationships":[{"character":"Théoden son of Thengel","relationship":"Son-in-law"},{"character":"Aragorn","relationship":"Affianced"},{"character":"Éomer son of Éomund","relationship":"Brother"}],"recentEvents":"Reported Aragorn's disappearance, discussed the Paths of the Dead"},{"name":"Gamling","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 7: HELM’S DEEP","c