alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 4: OF HERBS AND STEWED RABBIT","currentLocation":"Ithilien","description":"A massive creature of Harad, part of the battle","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Participated in the battle against Southrons"},{"name":"Samwise Gamgee","aliases":["Sam"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 10: THE CHOICES OF MASTER SAMWISE","currentLocation":"Near Cirith Ungol","description":"Frodo's loyal gardener and companion, carrying provisions and providing support.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Companion and Ring-bearer"},{"character":"Faramir","relationship":"Respects Faramir’s authority but challenges his accusations"},{"character":"Gollum","relationship":"Fighting"}],"recentEvents":"Fought Orcs to save Frodo, discovered Frodo was alive but captured"},{"name":"Anborn","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 6: THE FORBIDDEN POOL","currentLocation":"Henneth Annûn","description":"A scout under Faramir's command, reports unusual sightings in the wilderness.","relationships":[{"character":"Faramir","relationship":"Ordered to escort Gollum"}],"recentEvents":"Took Gollum away from Frodo and Faramir."},{"name":"Shelob","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 9: SHELOB’S LAIR","currentLocation":"Shelob’s Lair (Torech Ungol)","description":"A giant spider and predator, dwells in the dark tunnels near Cirith Ungol.","relationships":[{"character":"Frodo Baggins","relationship":"Attacking"}],"recentEvents":"Chased Frodo down the path, nearly capturing him"},{"name":"Denethor","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"Chapter 4: THE SIEGE OF GONDOR","currentLocation":"Silent Street","description":"Steward of Gondor, strategizes the defense against the enemy while grappling with internal conflict.","relationships":[{"character":"Gandalf the White","relationship":"Advisor and correspondent"},{"character":"Boromir","relationship":"Fa